#META# Translated from: Syriac (paraphrase)
#META# Date: between 810 and 830
#META# Ed_info: Lyons, Malcolm C. and Mattock, John N. (1978), Kitāb al-ajinna li-Buqrāṭ. Hippocrates :: On Embryos (On the Sperm and On the Nature of the Child) (Arabic Technical and Scientific Texts 7), Pembroke Arabic Texts, Cambridge, vol. 7, pp. 45-85

